<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Healthy Living Hub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Healthy Living Hub</h1>
        <p>Your go-to resource for reliable information on nutrition, exercise, and mental well-being.</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#nutrition">Nutrition</a></li>
            <li><a href="#exercise">Exercise</a></li>
            <li><a href="#mental-wellbeing">Mental Well-Being</a></li>
            <li><a href="#community">Community Support</a></li>
            <li><a href="#blog">Blog</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section id="nutrition">
            <h2>Nutrition</h2>
            <p>Explore healthy recipes and meal planning tips to nourish your body.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="exercise">
            <h2>Exercise</h2>
            <p>Find workout plans and tips to stay active and fit.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="mental-wellbeing">
            <h2>Mental Well-Being</h2>
            <p>Discover tips for maintaining mental health and well-being.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="community">
            <h2>Community Support</h2>
            <p>Join our forum to share experiences and advice with others on their health journeys.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="blog">
            <h2>Blog</h2>
            <p>Read success stories and articles that inspire healthy habits.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>Related Sites:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://www.healthline.com" target="_blank">Healthline</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.verywellfit.com" target="_blank">Verywell Fit</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Healthy Living Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
